{
 "name": "RPlog_SW1_Log_2001-04-06",
 "title": "Kidnapping Karrde to Safety",
 "summary": "Aboard the fleeing freighter Flippant Minion, Bazil McKenzie rouses a groggy, panicked Talon Karrde while Wedge pilots them away from a swarm of Griffon and Covenant attackers furious over the wrecked station. Bazil explains that Luke Skywalker ordered him to \"kidnap\" Karrde under a false bounty, sparing him a deadly meeting with Admiral Cimber on Selene and keeping his ties to the New Republic secret. Karrde, irritated but appreciative, radios his own crew via Toby and Orson to break off and stay clear, then helps talk their way out of the pursuit. Recognizing that the Republic Armed Forces ship is too large to outrun, Karrde contacts its commander Valen of the Covenant directly, persuading him to honor a decision to let them go, and the Minion finally slips past the gravity well and jumps to relative safety.",
